<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-EDITOR'S-CHOICE-ADVISORY-NYTSF </SLUG>
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; A Wasteland of Pseudo-Women's Culture &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Second Sexual Revolution &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Anti-Saddam &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The High Cost of TV Haunts All Politics &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; These articles _ which have already moved to Centerpiece
clients _ are now available as special one-shot buys.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; For rates and information on subscribing to Centerpiece,
contact one of these New York Times Syndicate sales
representatives: &LR;
</P>
<P>
   (--U.S. and Canada: DEBRA WEYDERT in New Jersey at
