<HEADLINE>
REPUBLICAN FOREIGN-POLICY PERSPECTIVES: MORALISTS VS. REALISTS 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By NORMAN LEVINE  
 c.2000 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; (RETRANSMITTING
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-02-22-00 1346EST &QL; 
</TRAILER>
</DOC>
<DOC>
