</P>
<P>
   REPUBS-PRIMARIES (Detroit) _ A Ledeall on Tuesday's Republican
primaries in Michigan, where the polls close at 8 p.m. EST, and
Arizona, with a poll-closing of 9 p.m. EST. By Richard L. Berke.
(1500 words).
</P>
