</P>
<P>
   BBA-HOLLEY-COLUMN (Sarasota, Fla.) _ As of now, Ken Griffey Jr.
is sitting pretty, in the middle of a powerful Reds lineup. By
Michael Holley.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
</TEXT>
