   COKE-BIAS _ ATLANTA _ Plaintiffs in the racial discrimination
lawsuit against Coca-Cola Co. are expected to file a motion today,
possibly related to the massive layoffs at the soft drink company.
(Unger, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
