   BBN-AVERY _ Steve Avery, a key member of the Atlanta Braves'
championship run during the early 1990's, has signed a minor-league
contract with the team and is expected to be in camp today. Avery,
the MVP of the 1991 National League Championship Series, spent last
season in Cincinnati after two years with the Boston Red Sox. If
