SAN FRANCISCO _  &UR; BAKEOFF  &LR; _ Forget the World Series, the Super Bowl
and the Final Four. The mother of all competitions hits San
Francisco Monday when 100 home cooks from across the country go
spatula-to-spatula in the 50th Annual Pillsbury Bake-Off. A cool
million-dollar grand prize will be awarded to the lucky winner.
<P>
   &UR; By Kim Severson &QL;  &LR; 
