<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    MICROSOFT WARNS JUDGE IN FINAL ROUND OF TRIAL
 &HT;    480&AMP;add. Moving in the (w) Washington and (f) financial
categories.
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ A Microsoft Corp. lawyer Tuesday urged U.S.
