of factors, including Alan Greenspan's attempts to slow down the
economy. By Kimberly Blanton. 1200 words.
</P>
<P>
   JUDGE-MICROSOFT (Washington) _ The government urges the judge in
the Microsoft case to find that the company violated the nation's
antitrust laws by wielding its enormous influence in the technology
industry to crush competitors and potential rivals. By Aaron
