<P>
   The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following general
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of
Wednesday, February 23 and thereafter. For questions about stories,
please contact Elizabeth Ferry at the Daily News at (818) 713-3702.
