<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-22 19:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5015 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u i BC-TAIWAN-CHINA-BOS &LR;      02-22 0851
