<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-22 21:42 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5148 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u p BC-PRIMARY-ANALYSIS-BOS &LR;      02-22 0856
